{"meta":{"title":"jie Zhou's Blog","subtitle":"一切节省，归根到底都归结为时间的节省","description":"","author":"Jie Zhou","url":"http://yoursite.com","root":"/"},"pages":[{"title":"","date":"2020-03-19T18:45:44.854Z","updated":"2020-03-19T18:45:44.854Z","comments":false,"path":"categories/index.html","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/categories/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""},{"title":"","date":"2020-03-19T18:48:15.607Z","updated":"2020-03-19T18:48:15.607Z","comments":false,"path":"tags/index.html","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/tags/index.html","excerpt":"","text":""}],"posts":[{"title":"GitHub的搭建博客的坑","slug":"GitHub的搭建博客的坑","date":"2020-03-19T19:25:24.000Z","updated":"2020-03-19T19:26:25.863Z","comments":true,"path":"2020/03/20/GitHub的搭建博客的坑/","link":"","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/03/20/GitHub%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%9D%91/","excerpt":"","text":"记录一些坑此次的坑是 GitHub下搭建Hexo博客的坑 关于访问 localhost:4000的坑网上很多人说改localhost为 127.0.0.1 亦或者是改端口为5000。但是我们要注意，根据官方文档Hexo服务器中说到Hexo 3.0 把服务器独立成了个别模块，您必须先安装 hexo-server 才能使用。 12345hexo version &#x2F;&#x2F;查询Hexo版本号npm install hexo-server --save &#x2F;&#x2F;安装hexokinase-serverhexo server &#x2F;&#x2F;启动服务器 您的网站会在 http:&#x2F;&#x2F;localhost:4000 下启动 如果你想更改端口号，或是执行遇到了EADDRINUSE错误，可在执行时使用-p选项指定其他端口1hexo server -p 5000 &#x2F;&#x2F;以更改端口为5000为例 还有一个坑是域名的问题。在/source目录下，创建一个记事本写入你绑定的域名时，切记保存文件名称为CNAME，并且是所有文件，然后把.txt后缀删掉 ==这是一个大坑== 如果你不这样做，会导致你每次git d 部署的时候你的博客会出现404访问错误！！！","categories":[{"name":"一些坑","slug":"一些坑","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/categories/%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E5%9D%91/"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo的坑","slug":"Hexo的坑","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/tags/Hexo%E7%9A%84%E5%9D%91/"}]},{"title":"test","slug":"test","date":"2020-03-19T18:31:27.000Z","updated":"2020-03-19T18:48:51.579Z","comments":true,"path":"2020/03/20/test/","link":"","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/03/20/test/","excerpt":"","text":"","categories":[{"name":"1","slug":"1","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/categories/1/"}],"tags":[{"na